### ============================================================
### Currencies — admin/internal scenarios
### Base URL: https://localhost:49609
###
### Read endpoints are anonymous.
### Create/Update/Delete require ManagingRole.
### Currency rates are synced by the CurrencyRateSyncTask job (NBP API).
###
### Note: route prefix is /api/currencies
### ============================================================

@baseUrl = https://localhost:49609
@token = YOUR_JWT_TOKEN
@contentType = application/json

# ============================================================
# AUTH
# ============================================================

### Login as admin
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "email": "admin@localhost",
  "password": "aDminN@W25!"
}

###

# ============================================================
# CURRENCIES
# ============================================================

### Get all currencies — paged (anonymous)
# Expected: 200 OK  →  CurrencyListVm
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/currencies?pageSize=10&pageNo=1
###

### Get all currencies — search
# Expected: 200 OK
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/currencies?searchString=EUR&pageSize=5&pageNo=1
###

### Get currency by id (anonymous)
# Expected: 200 OK  →  CurrencyVm
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/currencies/1
###

### Get currency — not found
# Expected: 404 Not Found
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/currencies/99999
###

### Create currency (ManagingRole)
# Expected: 201 Created  →  { "id": <newId> }
# Code must be a valid ISO 4217 code
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/currencies
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "code": "USD",
  "name": "US Dollar"
}
###

### Update currency (ManagingRole)
# Expected: 200 OK
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/currencies
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "id": 1,
  "code": "USD",
  "name": "United States Dollar"
}
###

### Delete currency (ManagingRole)
# Expected: 204 No Content
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/currencies/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
###

# ============================================================
# CURRENCY RATES
# ============================================================

### Get latest rate for currency
# Expected: 200 OK  →  CurrencyRateVm
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/currencies/1/rate/latest
###

### Get rate for specific day
# Expected: 200 OK  →  CurrencyRateVm
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/currencies/1/rate?date=2026-01-01
###
